63OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALI5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9b507904\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝爸打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話肉粉就冇甘好，但holistic個啲個植物油同碳水化合物偏高又會點"},{"pid":"8fefce13ee493550c7a17fe12b03053f3633b1d2","tid":56141,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:41:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你可以睇下呢個，有大部分貓糧比較<br />\n無穀都有好多種，最緊要自己知餵緊咪比主子食<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALI5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9b507904\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOmg<br />\n主子食緊solid gold無穀物抗敏<br />\n原來咁差？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食左大半年<br />\n係食呢隻先無屙爛屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎又要諗定轉咩糧了"},{"pid":"78da61d1cf5497a775322ddcd96a585dc9d349b1","tid":56141,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:42:24.000Z","msg":"我兩隻主人食canidae grain free都會爛便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50df254164391795e19a46c145045b2c093d4b1e","tid":56141,"uid":49549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T09:48:14.000Z","msg":"ZIWIPEAK 鹿肉乾+濕食左成年<br />\n食厭左 買左牛肉味 佢仲鐘意食<br />\n又平D <br />\n我真係好興奮"},{"pid":"fe643b2de7be41e5571d59500da18ccee6d8bc64","tid":56141,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:09:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你可以睇下呢個，有大部分貓糧比較<br />\n無穀都有好多種，最緊要自己知餵緊咪比主子食<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALI5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9b507904\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝爸打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話肉粉就冇甘好，但holistic個啲個植物油同碳水化合物偏高又會點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘅話有得揀會肉多過肉粉(meal)，肉粉營養無咁好<br />\n碳水化合物%高代表貓糧嘅植物成分高(穀類呀豆薯呢啲)<br />\n一嚟容易癡肥<br />\n二嚟植物蛋白高(會增加腎臟負擔)<br />\n<br />\n蛋白質同碳水化合物個%差唔多就多數溝左唔少植物蛋白"},{"pid":"c287add25921dd43aa4aa1a8022275a5b0903a28","tid":56141,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大佬食緊orijen 乾糧 + ziwipeak鹿肉罐頭<br />\n暫時幾好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n據說orijen 會生腎石<br />\nex 講既佢係獸晒<br />\n依家轉左canxxxxx 樓上講個隻</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打可唔可以講多啲點解會有腎石？<br />\n因為我睇唔少文章都係同水分唔夠有關<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實喺貓糧方面我唔信獸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為如果真係了解成分嘅話係唔會sell&quot;處方糧&quot;呢種咁差嘅糧<br />\n所以想知佢嘅理據係咩"},{"pid":"38fd5fd244cd7fc42cc7a5297945d5d42386c2d5","tid":56141,"uid":29818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>ZIWIPEAK 鹿肉乾+濕食左成年<br />\n食厭左 買左牛肉味 佢仲鐘意食<br />\n又平D <br />\n我真係好興奮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我主人三個月大 主濕食其實應該食幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪唔再放乾糧？"},{"pid":"f35d5e67086c310ab7982a002b4d92e7a79355d2","tid":56141,"uid":70206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T12:05:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你可以睇下呢個，有大部分貓糧比較<br />\n無穀都有好多種，最緊要自己知餵緊咪比主子食<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak&d=X8FF1IDY7L640IgtqOALI5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9b507904\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hjy163OufDpiu5Y1VlN1ATCVcehya2t2Xmu3_lKnJak</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝爸打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話肉粉就冇甘好，但holistic個啲個植物油同碳水化合物偏高又會點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘅話有得揀會肉多過肉粉(meal)，肉粉營養無咁好<br />\n碳水化合物%高代表貓糧嘅植物成分高(穀類呀豆薯呢啲)<br />\n一嚟容易癡肥<br />\n二嚟植物蛋白高(會增加腎臟負擔)<br />\n<br />\n蛋白質同碳水化合物個%差唔多就多數溝左唔少植物蛋白</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後好似oven baked個無榖雞肉同wellness core 最好<br />\n<br />\n不過wellness個protein去到49.4，會唔會太高"},{"pid":"63a07d5863fae2318aeaab9a119095be0edf1861","tid":56141,"uid":21654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T03:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝爸打分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似話肉粉就冇甘好，但holistic個啲個植物油同碳水化合物偏高又會點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我嘅話有得揀會肉多過肉粉(meal)，肉粉營養無咁好<br />\n碳水化合物%高代表貓糧嘅植物成分高(穀類呀豆薯呢啲)<br />\n一嚟容易癡肥<br />\n二嚟植物蛋白高(會增加腎臟負擔)<br />\n<br />\n蛋白質同碳水化合物個%差唔多就多數溝左唔少植物蛋白</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇完之後好似oven baked個無榖雞肉同wellness core 最好<br />\n<br />\n不過wellness個protein去到49.4，會唔會太高</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實你睇番罐頭嘅蛋白質閒閒地都7，80%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我主子之前食chicken soup幼貓糧(40%)<br />\n之後轉左thrive個半月(57.8%)，夜晚thrive或者canagan罐<br />\n初初啲便好軟爛，要keep住同佢地玩，消耗蛋白質<br />\n慢慢習慣左就正常<br />\n同埋高蛋白質糧要跟份量餵，餵多左會爛便，因為用唔晒"}]}